-- Monti’s Tax Review Endorsed by IMF as Significant Improvement
-- B y   A n d r e w   F r y e
-- 2012-10-01T14:12:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-01/monti-s-tax-review-endorsed-by-imf-as-significant-improvement.html
Italian Prime Minister  Mario Monti ’s
review of the country’s tax policy was endorsed by the
International Monetary Fund.  The review “provides a framework for significant
structural improvement,” the IMF said today in a report
distributed by the Italian Finance Ministry.  To contact the reporter on this story:
